attachments.title: A Sunken Nazi Sub Has Been Discovered Off The Texas Coast
attachments.text: In a shocking reminder of how close the Second World War came to America, a German U-boat has been discovered by marine archaeologists working off the shores of Texas in the Gulf of Mexico.
attachments.fallback: io9: A Sunken Nazi Sub Has Been Discovered Off The Texas Coast
